text: SV Waldhof Mannheim is a German football club. It is in Mannheim, Baden- Württemberg. The club was founded 1907. The club today has over 2,400 people. The team plays in the Regionalliga Süd the 4th German Football division. == Other websites == *Official website Category:1907 establishments in Germany Category:Football clubs in Baden-Württemberg Category:Mannheim
